reviews.text: New location at HKG, great value breakfast with tasty chicken noodle soup and warm soy milk.

The xiaolongbao and other dumplings were good, and, although tasty, the fried fish was too bony. 

Nice selection of food with an easy-to-use bilingual menu with pictures.

There is plenty of seating including private rooms but the air-conditioning is very fierce.
Super authentic Chinese quizine and our waiter was also great Samuel the place was really busy great food.
Meh...was expecting a lot better. Tofu was bland...they did have a great fish which is why they are getting three stars...service was good. Again though, I had higher expectations.
Michellin Star, good service but just okay food for its price.

result.name: 蘇浙匯

reviews.text:
Visited this place with one other person. Ambience was cosy and for slightly more privacy, we asked for the sofa seat. Food in general met my expectation of shanghainese dishes.  

I do enjoy a few items from the menu. Braised fish maw in abalone sauce, Jasmin Tea smoke duck (best to have it when it is still hot) and Green tea iced cake to round up the meal. Do check with staff whats good to order on that day of visit.
value for money, good food and service
Great food and Great service!!!
Great food and exceptional service, food could get to very expensive if ordering seafood. Otherwise, great value for the quality.
I expected to be blown away, but nothing to write home about. Good, but not that good.

reviews.text: 調味適中，價錢合理，招呼不錯，有二小時泊車

Visited this place with one other person. Ambience was cosy and for slightly more privacy, we asked for the sofa seat. Food in general met my expectation of shanghainese dishes.  

I do enjoy a few items from the menu. Braised fish maw in abalone sauce, Jasmin Tea smoke duck (best to have it when it is still hot) and Green tea iced cake to round up the meal. Do check with staff whats good to order on that day of visit.
雖然地方好難停車，但係食物質素超高。最好係人多啲搵個包廳，10個八個人靜靜地食靚野飲靚酒。記得提前訂位，尤其是午餐
食咗幾年幾次，變化不大，但仍好食，今日推介，沙煱雲吞鷄
